          <h1><a href="limited-time-stellantis-incentives-live.html">Limited-Time Stellantis Incentives are Live – Get Mobile with Curbee</a></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <span> Written by <a class="author-link" href="author/curbee%3FhsLang=en.html">Curbee</a> | May 08, 2025 </span>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-section">
          <span><p><span><strong><span>As a Trusted Mopar Partner, Curbee Enables Stellantis Dealers to Launch or Level Up Mobile Service to Capture Incentives </span></strong></span></p>
<p>Stellantis is making it easier than ever by offering significant funding to help fast-acting Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, Ram and Fiat dealers add or up their game in the revenue-generating business line of mobile service, if they act this month. Curbee, a technology company that enables dealers to offer mobile service with its AI powered scheduling platform, customer-facing scheduling tool, technician-facing mobile app, and hands-on support, is one of the Mopar-approved vendors and is ready to act fast to help dealers claim their benefits.</p>
<p>“This is a fantastic opportunity for Stellantis dealers to launch mobile service or enhance their programs, with significant financial assistance from the manufacturer,” Curbee CEO Amit Chandarana. “Mobile service is a no-brainer convenience for customers, and now it's a revenue and retention generating no-brainer for dealers with minimal capital investment. It’s a way to add new service capacity without adding new bays. And the latest offer from Stellantis eliminates a significant portion of the program startup cost. The time is right to add mobile service and we’re super excited to be a part of the program.”</p>
<p>For Stellantis dealers, Curbee makes mobile service easy to launch and scale – because we’ve built our entire platform around it. As an Mopar Partner, we have the tools, experience, and support to help you take full advantage of Stellantis’ limited-time offer.&nbsp;</p>
<p>On May 5, Mopar announced the following financial and marketing assistance for the first dealers to act and have plans in place by May 31, 2025, in two categories, those with existing Mopar mobile service and those adding mobile service for the first time.</p>
<p>Here’s what Stellantis dealers can expect with the current offer:&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>Support for upfitting and branding your mobile service vehicle</li>
<li>Cover up to 50% of Curbee’s M.A.R.S. (Mobile and Remote Service) platform monthly costs)</li>
<li>Marketing assistance to promote your new service</li>
<li>Additional benefits for both new and existing mobile service programs</li>
<li>Requirements designed to set you up for long-term success</li>
</ul>
<p>Curbee’s team is ready to act fast to help interested dealers be the first to take advantage of the Stellantis deal. For help getting started, email hello@curbee.com.</p>
<p><strong>About Curbee</strong><strong><br></strong>Curbee is the fastest-growing mobile service technology provider. Curbee enables dealerships to offer mobile service with its platform called M.A.R.S. (Mobile and Remote Service). With Curbee M.A.R.S., it's simple: dealerships send the right van to the right job, using the right route with the right parts, at the right time.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Our street credit comes from our in-market experience and best practices. With our software, solutions and success team, dealers can scale mobile service quickly, delivering a game-changing customer experience while driving revenue growth. Our innovative technology supports AI-powered scheduling &amp; analytics, ensuring dealers efficiently “go mobile.” Curbee’s team has highly relevant experience from Tesla, Toyota, Ford and Roadster and is backed by DVx Ventures, a venture studio with a unique approach to company creation and scaling. For more information, visit&nbsp;<a href="http://www.curbee.com/"><span>www.curbee.com</span></a>.</p><amp-analytics type="gtag"><script type="application/json">{
